title: Green Wing - series 2 episodes 1 - 8
description:
A British television series from 2006, series 1 was from 2004.

Wonderfully disfunctional hospital based sketch, comedy , drama, series featuring quirky characters including the insecure and perverted Dr. Statham and the bizarre nymphomaniac HR manager Sue White. The whole cast is great and the show is original, funny and off the wall.

Revued on imdb at  <a href=" http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0423661/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0423661/</a>   and given 9.1/10.

Episodes are in divx format with a run time of about 50 minutes each.
